        I_NEVER_THOUGHT_IT_WOULD_BE_YOU_TWO                                  = 7421,  -- I never thought it would be you two who helped me.
        I_TOO_HAVE_SOME_VERY_IMPORTANT_BUSINESS_ON                           = 7422,  -- I, too, have some very important business on the other side of that door.
        AH_WHAT_A_GRAND_SIGHT                                                = 7423,  -- Ah, what a grand sight...
        THE_FIVE_MOTHERCRYSTALS_IT_IS_THIS_CONTRAPTION_THAT                  = 7424,  -- The five mothercrystals... It is this contraption that protects them as they slumber beneath Vana'diel.
        PROTECTS_THEM_SO_THAT_IS_THE_PURPOSE_OF                              = 7425,  -- Protects them...? So, that is the purpose of this tower!?
        EXACTLY_THE_FIVE_CRYSTALS_ARE_CONNECTED_BY_THE                       = 7426,  -- Exactly. The five crystals are connected by the five Crystal Lines that all converge on this very place.
        FOR_MANY_CENTURIES_WE_HAVE_MONITORED_THE_LINES                       = 7427,  -- For many centuries we have monitored the lines...protected the radiance of the crystals.
        HOWEVER_WHEN_THE_WYRMKING_BAHAMUT_ARRIVED_THE_FIVE                   = 7428,  -- However, when the Wyrmking, Bahamut, arrived, the five crystal lines began acting strangely. We could no longer control them.
        AND_THEN_CAME_SELH_TEUS                                              = 7429,  -- And then came Selh'teus.
        HE_CAME_HERE                                                         = 7430,  -- He came...here?
        SIR_NAG_MOLADA_ARE_YOU_SAYING_THAT_THE                               = 7431,  -- Sir Nag'molada! Are you saying that the boy came here via the Crystal Line!?
        WHICH_MEANS_BY_TRAVELING_BACK_THROUGH_THE_LINE                       = 7432,  -- Which means, by traveling back through the line, he can...
        EXACTLY_HE_CAN_REACH_THE_FIFTH_CRYSTAL_HOWEVER                       = 7433,  -- Exactly. He can reach the fifth crystal. However, it is not as easy as you may think. The lines were not built as a path for men.
        THEY_WERE_BUILT_TO_GATHER_THE_LIGHT_OF                               = 7434,  -- They were built to gather the light of the mothercrystals.
        THE_TRUE_REASON_SELH_TEUS_WAS_ABLE_TO                                = 7435,  -- The true reason Selh'teus was able to enter this place was because he was aided by a guardian of the crystals--a terrestrial avatar.
        A_TERRESTRIAL_AVATAR                                                 = 7436,  -- A terrestrial avatar...?
        IT_IS_ALL_CLEAR_NOW_PHOENIX_LED_ME                                   = 7437,  -- It is all clear now! Phoenix led me to this place to show me the way to the celestial capital of Al'Taieu!
        PHOENIX_LED_YOU_HERE_THAT_IS_TRULY_UNFORTUNATE                       = 7438,  -- Phoenix? Led you here? That is truly unfortunate. If this only had happened before Pso'Xja was reactivated...
        REACTIVATED_WHAT_DO_YOU_MEAN_BY_THAT_NAG                             = 7439,  -- Reactivated...? What do you mean by that, Nag'molada?
        THE_RUINS_OF_PSO_XJA_WERE_ONCE_THE                                   = 7440,  -- The ruins of Pso'Xja were once the homes of my Kuluu brothers and sisters. However, at the onset of the Kuluu war with the Zilart, the terrestrial avatars lent us their power and helped transform the area into an impenetrable stronghold.
        AND_DEEP_BELOW_THE_RUINS_IS_A_DEVICE                                 = 7441,  -- And deep below the ruins is a device that blocks the flow of energy through the Crystal Line. Esha'ntarl has repaired that device...
        REPAIRED_IT_WHY_WOULD_SHE_DO_SUCH_A                                  = 7442,  -- Repaired it! Why would she do such a thing!?
        I_NO_LONGER_KNOW_WHAT_THE_SOCIETY_IS                                 = 7443,  -- I no longer know what the society is plotting. That is why I came here--to find out their true intentions!
        ID_7444                                                              = 7444,  -- ...
        HA_HA_HA_ARE_YOU_SURPRISED                                           = 7445,  -- Ha ha ha! Are you surprised?
        I_GUESS_THAT_TO_YOU_WE_ANCIENTS_KULUU                                = 7446,  -- I guess that to you we ancients--Kuluu and Zilart--are all the same. However, that could not be further from the truth.
        THE_ZILART_WERE_BLESSED_WITH_THE_ABILITY_TO                          = 7447,  -- The Zilart were blessed with the ability to subliminally communicate with all those around them--they possessed the whisper of the soul. It was this ability that made the bonds between them unbreakable.
        HOWEVER_THERE_WERE_THOSE_WHO_WERE_BORN_WITHOUT                       = 7448,  -- However, there were those who were born without the whisper--the Kuluu. My people were destined from birth to sit outside the bonds of the Zilartian community.
        BUT_WE_BYSTANDERS_WERE_ABLE_TO_ASCERTAIN_THE                         = 7449,  -- But we bystanders were able to ascertain the truth, and it was this that helped us survive the crusades of ten thousand years ago.
        THE_ZILART_THE_TERRESTRIAL_AVATARS_SELH_TEUS_ONCE                    = 7450,  -- The Zilart, the terrestrial avatars, Selh'teus... Once again, their sins will deface Vana'diel and undermine her children.
        THAT_IS_TERRIBLE_IF_YOU_KNOW_OF_SUCH                                 = 7451,  -- That is terrible! If you know of such a battle brewing, why do you not attempt to stop it!?
        WHY_MUST_WE_FIGHT_THE_AVATARS_SUCH_A                                 = 7452,  -- Why must we fight the avatars!? Such a battle would be meaningless! Our true enemies are the Emptiness and the evil boy that is spreading it!
        HAH_IS_THAT_WHAT_YOU_HAVE_TO_SAY                                     = 7453,  -- Hah. Is that what you have to say? Tenzen, when are you going to stop being led around on a leash like a measly dog? When are you going to see what the terrestrial avatars really want?
        LISTEN_I_TOLD_YOU_THIS_ONCE_BEFORE_SELH                              = 7454,  -- Listen. I told you this once before. Selh'teus is nothing but a traitor.
        TEN_THOUSAND_YEARS_AGO_HE_PREVENTED_THE_ZILART                       = 7455,  -- Ten thousand years ago, he prevented the Zilart from obtaining what they desired. Now, he is simply attempting the same thing.
        THE_RECORDS_STORED_IN_THIS_CRYSTAL_LINE_OBSERVATION                  = 7456,  -- The records stored in this Crystal Line observation equipment have shown me the reason why Selh'teus travels to the mothercrystals.
        BY_TOUCHING_THE_SHARDS_HE_IS_ABLE_TO                                 = 7457,  -- By touching the shards, he is able to drain their light...their power.
        THE_CRYSTAL_S_POWER                                                  = 7458,  -- The crystal's power?
        TO_ACCOMPLISH_OUR_TASK_WE_HAD_TO_GATHER                              = 7459,  -- To accomplish our task, we had to gather the power of the crystals and fuse it into one.
        AND_TO_DO_THAT_WE_NEEDED_TO_REPAIR                                   = 7460,  -- And to do that, we needed to repair and revive the Zilartian machines that were damaged in the accident that occurred ten thousand years ago. With the machines working again, we were able to slowly draw the light of the crystals.
        WHEN_HE_REALIZED_HE_COULD_NOT_SINGLE_HANDEDLY                        = 7461,  -- When he realized he could not single-handedly take on the whole nation of Jeuno, he turned to the crystals instead. And when he laid his hands upon them, their power flowed from the facets like water rushing from a broken dam. This sudden loss of power resulted in a disruption in the space surrounding the crystals...
        WITHOUT_THE_LIFE_GIVING_LIGHT_OF_THE_CRYSTALS                        = 7462,  -- Without the life-giving light of the crystals shining upon it, the space became overwhelmed with darkness--with Emptiness.
        BUT_SELH_TEUS_FIRST_APPEARED_ON_VANA_DIEL                            = 7463,  -- But, Selh'teus first appeared on Vana'diel the same time as Bahamut.
        IN_MY_HOME_NATION_THERE_WERE_MANY_REPORTS                            = 7464,  -- In my home nation, there were many reports of the Emptiness eating its way through the land, long before Bahamut even arrived...
        WAIT_YOU_JUST_SAID_THAT_YOU_WERE_SLOWLY                              = 7465,  -- Wait! You just said that you were slowly drawing the light of the crystals...
        THAT_WOULD_MEAN_THAT_THE_CAUSE_OF_THE                                = 7466,  -- That would mean that the cause of the Emptiness in the East is you--the Zilart!
        HMPH_I_WAS_BEGINNING_TO_WONDER_WHEN_YOU                              = 7467,  -- Hmph. I was beginning to wonder when you would realize that, Tenzen.
        BUT_DON_T_MISUNDERSTAND_US_IT_WAS_NEVER                              = 7468,  -- But don't misunderstand us. It was never our intention to harm Vana'diel with the Emptiness.
        WHILE_WE_LAY_IN_SLUMBER_FOR_THE_PAST                                 = 7469,  -- While we lay in slumber for the past ten thousand years, things changed. The crystals changed.
        ESPECIALLY_THE_FIFTH_CRYSTAL_DEEP_BELOW_AL_TAIEU                     = 7470,  -- Especially the fifth crystal, deep below Al'Taieu.
        WHEN_THE_CELESTIAL_CAPITAL_WAS_DESTROYED_AND_SUNK                    = 7471,  -- When the celestial capital was destroyed and sunk to the bottom of the sea, the crystal was damaged. The data that it returns is very odd indeed.
        HOWEVER_YOU_NEED_NOT_WORRY_ONCE_THE_GATE                             = 7472,  -- However, you need not worry. Once the Gate of the Gods is opened, the crystals will return to their former state.
        AND_ONCE_THEY_DO_THE_EMPTINESS_WILL_DISAPPEAR                        = 7473,  -- And once they do, the Emptiness will disappear in the crystal's radiance, and the Zilart will have accomplished their dream.
        ONLY_THE_WRETCHED_TERRESTRIAL_AVATARS_STAND_IN_OUR                   = 7474,  -- Only the wretched terrestrial avatars stand in our way...!
